Your feet are made for walking – so let’s keep them healthy. This workshop
will teach you all you need to know about checking and caring for your feet.
In this practical workshop you will learn about:
* How high blood glucose levels affect your feet
* Daily foot care and protecting your feet
* How to prevent infection and foot complications
